ium_2x.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\n                    \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1442px)\" srcset=\"https://www.apple.com/newsroom/images/2025/01/apple-miami-worldcenter-opens-to-excited-customers-in-downtown-miami/article/Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-first-customers_Full-Bleed-Image.jpg.xlarge.jpg, https://www.apple.com/newsroom/images/2025/01/apple-miami-worldcenter-opens-to-excited-customers-in-downtown-miami/article/Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-first-customers_Full-Bleed-Image.jpg.xlarge_2x.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\n                    \n                        \u003cimg src=\"https://www.apple.com/newsroom/images/2025/01/apple-miami-worldcenter-opens-to-excited-customers-in-downtown-miami/article/Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-first-customers_Full-Bleed-Image.jpg.large.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.apple.com/newsroom/images/2025/01/apple-miami-worldcenter-opens-to-excited-customers-in-downtown-miami/article/Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-first-customers_Full-Bleed-Image.jpg.large_2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\" alt=\"\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \n                \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n                \n                \n                 \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/newsroom/images/2025/01/apple-miami-worldcenter-opens-to-excited-customers-in-downtown-miami/article/Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-first-customers.zip\" download=\"\" data-analytics-title=\"download image - Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-first-customers_Full-Bleed-Image\" aria-label=\"Download image, A smiling customer walks into Apple Miami Worldcenter, with team members cheering.\"\u003e\n                    Download image\n                \u003c/a\u003e\n                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv\u003eTeam members at Apple Miami Worldcenter welcome the store’s first customers.\n                    \u003c/div\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/newsroom/images/2025/01/apple-miami-worldcenter-opens-to-excited-customers-in-downtown-miami/article/Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-first-customers.zip\" download=\"\" data-analytics-title=\"download image - Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-first-customers_Full-Bleed-Image\" aria-label=\"Download media, A smiling customer walks into Apple Miami Worldcenter, with team members cheering.\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    \n\n\n     \n     \n    \n    \n        \u003cdiv data-component-list=\"ModalGalleryTrigger\"\u003e\n             \n                 \u003cdiv\u003eApple’s newest store in Miami opened this Friday, January 24, in the city’s dynamic downtown district, where customers and members of the local community celebrated with the over 150-person-strong store team.\n\u003c/div\u003e\n                 \n             \n                 \u003cdiv\u003eShoppers can easily and seamlessly upgrade to iPhone 16 by taking advantage of Apple Trade In, various financing offers, carrier activation, and personalized setup — all in a uniquely designed store where everyone is welcome. Customers can shop the all-new lineup of iPhone 16, Mac, MacBook Pro, Mac mini powered by the M4 chip, Apple Watch Series 10, and AirPods models, and receive personalized shopping support from Apple team members.\n\u003c/div\u003e\n                 \n             \n                 \u003cdiv\u003eTo celebrate the opening of the store, Apple Miami Worldcenter will offer customized Today at Apple sessions highlighting the store’s environment-centered design and natural elements, as well as special Made for Business events led by small business owners. Customers can explore upcoming Today at Apple sessions and book at \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/retail/miamiworldcenter/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eapple.com/retail/miamiworldcenter\u003c/a\u003e.\n\u003c/div\u003e\n                 \n             \n         \u003c/div\u003e\n \n\n    \n    \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n    \n    \n    \n    \n      \u003cfigure aria-label=\"Media, Apple’s Deirdre O’Brien and Eddy Cue greet customers at Apple Miami Worldcenter.\" data-component-list=\"ModalGalleryTrigger\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n             \n              \n              \u003cdiv\u003e\n                Apple’s Deirdre O’Brien and Eddy Cue greet customers in front of Apple Miami Worldcenter.\n              \u003c/div\u003e\n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/newsroom/images/2025/01/apple-miami-worldcenter-opens-to-excited-customers-in-downtown-miami/article/Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-Deirdre-O-Brien-and-Eddy-Cue-welcome-customers.zip\" download=\"\" data-analytics-title=\"download image - Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-Deirdre-O-Brien-and-Eddy-Cue-welcome-customers_big\" aria-label=\"Download media, Apple’s Deirdre O’Brien and Eddy Cue greet customers at Apple Miami Worldcenter.\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/figure\u003e\n    \n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n    \n    \n    \n    \n      \u003cfigure aria-label=\"Media, Excited customers line up outside of Apple Miami Worldcenter.\" data-component-list=\"ModalGalleryTrigger\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n             \n              \n              \u003cdiv\u003e\n                Excited customers line up outside the new store, located in Miami’s buzzy downtown district.\n              \u003c/div\u003e\n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/newsroom/images/2025/01/apple-miami-worldcenter-opens-to-excited-customers-in-downtown-miami/article/Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-store-exterior.zip\" download=\"\" data-analytics-title=\"download image - Apple-Miami-Worldcenter-opening-day-store-exterior_big\" a